1. *Toliko* ljudi je bilo na proslavi da smo se gurali. (So many people were at the celebration that we were pushing.)
2. *Toliko* sam se trudio da bih se istakao, ali nisam uspeo. (I tried so hard to stand out, but I didn't succeed.)
3. On je čuo *toliko* priča da nije znao šta da misli. (He heard so many stories that he didn't know what to think.)
4. Ona je *toliko* jela da je izgledala puno. (She ate so much that she looked full.)
5. *Toliko* je toga što nisam znao o njoj da sam se iznenadio. (So much I didn't know about her that I was surprised.)